snippet.title: Jumbo Jet Pilot for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

Jumbo Jet Pilot is a flight simulation, in which you steer a Jumbo Jet and fly to a certain destination and land there.

The game offers 5 levels of difficulty and you can play either in daytime or nighttime.


What I think:

To be honest, I can't say much about this game except for that the manual isn't so good IMHO. It is somewhat helpful, but I had to figure to out most parts by myself.

Anyways, I don't know how to fly properly or where to (I suppose it was the lower right corner of the map?), so yeah...this gameplay video might be boring to someone...
